{"type": "article", "id": 57830, "title": "古根海姆为艺术家出的联名周边，非常迷人｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2018-10-30T22:43:54Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 768, "name": "产品设计"}, {"id": 53820, "name": "Guggenheim Store"}, {"id": 44634, "name": "Hive"}, {"id": 53821, "name": "fuseproject"}, {"id": 47964, "name": "Warm Nordic"}, {"id": 53822, "name": "OGSB Studio"}, {"id": 5706, "name": "Sonos"}, {"id": 53823, "name": "Hilma af Klint"}, {"id": 9226, "name": "Yves Béhar"}, {"id": 47968, "name": "Hans Olsen"}, {"id": 53824, "name": "Barry McGee"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 122, "image": "img/article/article_show/20181030212028qcLCEV4hufWRrbGt.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; color: #000000; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none} span.s3 {font: 11.0px 'PingFang SC'; font-kerning: none} span.s4 {text-decoration: underline ; font-kerning: none} span.s5 {font: 11.0px Helvetica; font-kerning: none; color: #0f1419; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #0f1419} span.s6 {font-kerning: none; color: #0f1419; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #0f1419} span.s7 {font-kerning: none; color: #333333; -webkit-text-stroke: 0px #333333} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Hilma af Klint-inspired collection by Guggenheim Store</h3><p>10 月，纽约古根海姆博物馆举办了瑞典抽象艺术家 Hilma af Klint 的首次大型个展，呈现她作品中的构图、版式和文化趋向，以此展示她对抽象艺术的开创性作用。她的作品善用大胆的色调和不拘的形式，融入了神智学、通灵学、进化论、原子理论等元素，却又因太过于前卫，直到 1980 年代才得到人们的认同。</p><p>为庆祝展览，纽约古根海姆博物馆创作了一系列独家时装、家居用品、文具和珠宝作品，灵感来自于 Hilma af Klint 的作品。该系列产品主要由女性工匠和设计师创作，产品范围从陶瓷花瓶、烛架到围巾、T恤、包袋和手表，糅合了几何形状和明丽的色彩。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181030213415E8w9lxMBufoJAjmP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181030212145VYAyHk4rNW2oKugD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.612798\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181030212145bE60dBDSA15sLgKp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.612798\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181030212146aFDeiWSzgHql5Ex8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.612798\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201810302121466TXfOmcGasPSQLEo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.612798\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201810302121473Fy8b9VIeTD1ruSW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.908904\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201810302121458MYIEs2tAP0OcHqU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.612798\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://www.wallpaper.com/lifestyle/hilma-af-klint-collection-at-guggenheim-store\" rel=\"nofollow\">Wallpaper*</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Hive View Outdoor by fuseproject and Hive</h3><p>Hive View 户外摄像头是与设计师和 fuseproject 的创始人 Yves Béhar 合作的产物，展示了一种独特的“抓取和移动”功能，让你可以将轻量级相机模块从固定支架上分离出来，并将其放置在需要的其他地方。他简洁时尚的外观足够引人注目。</p><p>基本安装和壁挂安装使用户可以根据自己的喜好设置一个角度，130 度视野有助于并且可以选择将其从安装座上卸下并无线使用。用户可以根据需要下载和分享视频，图像质量也不错，根据信号强度，可选择 720p 或 1080p 最大分辨率。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181030212416xfmwG1iPeM7Qsc54.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.612798\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181030212416BvrwqTVYCi6gdFkL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.874658\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181030212416VIbevUKH7PhN1Z2O.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.613014\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://fuseproject.com/work/british-gas/hive-view/?focus=overview\" rel=\"nofollow\">fuseproject</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Hans Olsen’s Iconic Balloon Lounge Chair by Warm Nordic</h3><p>这是丹麦品牌 Warm Nordic 第一次推出“经典大师”系列，丹麦建筑师兼工业设计师 Hans Olsen 是其大师系列之一，他是 20 世纪中期现代主义浪潮中较为神秘的重要人物。</p><p>这把翻新推出的 Hans Olsen 的名作 Balloon 休闲椅，它是一个带有锥形坐凳的绒面革休闲椅，结合了细长的金属腿和简单木制扶手。之字形支撑腿将座位与椅子框架连接起来，确保椅子的舒适度。到目前为止，Balloon 休闲椅的原版已经很难找到，它可能会偶尔出现在二手家具市场上，标着极其昂贵的价格。但 Warm Nordic 此次将其翻新推出，则给了现代主义设计爱好者提供了一个购入经典之作的良机。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181030212947uHAdNy3gBRaJTSMe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181030212947DvW15pQUg9LZ4fez.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.043750\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181030212948ih02Xk7MGplR3sIY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181030212948SmR85nJYMEH0GKTy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201810302129484aGcdntDBu2CQKWI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.511719\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181030212948YSMcWX7iZhPb23p6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://design-milk.com/warm-nordic-releases-hans-olsens-iconic-balloon-lounge-chair-from-1955/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Design Milk</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Gota Collection by OGSB Studio</h3><p>OGSB Studio 是一家位于布鲁塞尔的设计工作室，最近他们与 Ateliers J＆J 合作开发了一组由当地制造商生产的再生铝制成的灯具 Gota 系列。</p><p>Gota 系列包括台灯和落地灯，每个都设有旋转运动的两个点，分别位于灯的“手臂”和灯罩为止，满足更多场景的使用需求。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181030213117oWtru9cCsb04kIzQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.570313\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181030213117iHGZ27lWUCzKQNm5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181030213117o8ugrReviDA6Cwq7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667188\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181030213118oGYMWSAHf5Iji7pk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.499219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201810302131195OiknEcb3tBGNw86.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.496875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181030213120ajn9SvRbzmsg0ut1.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563235\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：<a href=\"https://ogsbstudio.com/#/gota-collection/\" rel=\"nofollow\">OGSB Studio</a></figcaption></figure></div><h3>Sonos Play:5 Beastie Boys Edition by Beastie Boys</h3><p>为庆祝自传发行，Beastie Boys 乐队的 Mike D 和 Ad-Rock 选用涂鸦艺术家 Barry McGee 的作品设计出限量版 Play:5 音响。</p><p>Barry McGee 表示：“音箱的设计非常简洁现代，所以我采用了一种图案来颠覆音响传统的正面外观，同时仍能为它锦上添花。”音箱内部是六个装有标准规格驱动器的扩音器。</p><p>这款音响承载着该乐队的传奇经历，并再现了他们对音乐、艺术和流行文化颠覆性的影响。所得款项将以 Adam Yauch 基金会的名义捐赠给 Peace Sisters 和 Little Kids Rock。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181030213253sAY7M0vIlfu1LQaq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.733594\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181030213253EuGWkHFARwXp7jbC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667188\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20181030213255wjV2OBukZfSFQeHi.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.703125\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">图片来源：Sonos</figcaption></figure></div>"}